name: Control Point Generation
description: As the world becomes more and more digital, cryptocurrency is the next natural step in monetary development. CPG is a decentralized public chain generated by the control points of the encrypted digital path protection group. On the basis of supporting high-frequency transactions, it realizes the compatibility of intelligent contracts. In the future, it will become a basic platform for carrying users, assets and application security. CpG represents an important step in the adoption of global cryptocurrency.
